Plateform: OSX

Resolution: 1024*680

Compilation: type "make" to compile the file

Reproduction: type ./RayTracer.o -input test/input-01

Features: Rendering on polygons and ellipsoid, Phong shading, reflection, shadowing, 2 point light source and 2 directional light source, applied linear transformations including translate, scale and rotate.

Output: image-01.png 

running time: around 60 minutes